### ========== 用户服务测试 ==========

### 1. 注册用户
POST http://localhost:8081/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "test",
    "password": "123456",
    "role": "ADMIN"
}

### 2. 登录（拿到 Token）
POST http://localhost:8081/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "zhangsan",
    "password": "123456"
}

### 3. 带 Token 访问受保护接口（替换成上一步返回的 token）
GET http://localhost:8081/api/user/7
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI3Iiwicm9sZSI6InN0dWRlbnQiLCJpYXQiOjE3ODA0MTA2NTUsImV4cCI6MTc4MTAxNTQ1NX0.nUCml3oI__EySyYQV4a9oA8hXJGLx51k0X4AvqlI8PY

### 4. 不带 Token 访问 → 应返回 401
GET http://localhost:8081/api/user/1

### 5. 带无效 Token 访问 → 应返回 401 Invalid token
GET http://localhost:8081/api/user/1
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token_123